<p>在 VisualStudio 2015 和 VisualStudio 2017 微软支持在 xmal 使用 region</p>

<div class="language-csharp highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>  <span class="p">&lt;!--</span><span class="err">#</span><span class="n">region</span> <span class="n">xx</span><span class="p">--&gt;</span>
 
      <span class="err">代码</span>

  <span class="p">&lt;!--</span><span class="err">#</span><span class="n">endregion</span><span class="p">--&gt;</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p><img src="http://image.acmx.xyz/65fb6078-c169-4ce3-cdd9-e35752d07be0%2F2018315112517.jpg" alt="" /></p>

<p>把上面的代码折叠，请看下面</p>

<p><img src="http://image.acmx.xyz/65fb6078-c169-4ce3-cdd9-e35752d07be0%2F2018315112629.jpg" alt="" /></p>

<p>如果觉得这个不好用，推荐插件<a href="https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=JacobJohnston.XAMLRegions">XAML Regions</a></p>

